Package: PeakSegDisk
Type: Package
Title: Disk-based Implementation of PeakSegFPOP
Version: 2018.09.28
Author: Toby Dylan Hocking
Maintainer: Toby Dylan Hocking <toby.hocking@r-project.org>
Description: Disk-based implementation of PeakSegFPOP
 <arXiv:1703.03352> for single-sample peak calling
 (independantly for each sample and genomic problem),
 can handle huge data sets (10^7 or more).
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: db_stl
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: data.table (>= 1.9.8), namedCapture, parallel
Suggests: testthat, httr, ggplot2

